            <section ID="id_link_4efd92d9-f2b0-8fc7-e063-6294a90ab590">
               <id root="4efd92d9-f2af-8fc7-e063-6294a90ab590"/>
               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Apply 1 patch at a time to the affected area up to 3 times per day. Do not leave on skin for more than a total of 8 hours per day. 
  <br/>
Children under 12 years of age: consult a doctor. Supervise children when using this product. May take 1-2 weeks to produce benefcial effects. Ask a health care professional or physician for use beyond 6 weeks.
  <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="img_4efd926f-3089-c4e8-e063-6394a90aed50"/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20260407"/>
               <component>
                  <observationMedia ID="img_4efd926f-3089-c4e8-e063-6394a90aed50">
                     <text>up to 3 times a day</text>
